plotInformation.title: Grand Slam Championships by Player
plotInformation.caption: This plot shows the overlap of tennis Grand Slam tournament winners. Notably, the majority of champions have won only at one tournament venue. Out of 117 champions, only 9 have won at least once at every Grand Slam tournament venue.
